{"tid":2027600,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(劇透慎入) 我chaos;child進度已經去到11章  開始有d驚 唔敢睇結局","createTime":"2020-05-21T12:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T17:06:41.000Z","uid":6327,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c886fecdff9a158e8a64177744d083430ce19c97","tid":2027600,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:36:46.000Z","msg":"雖然當初有睇過動畫打底<br />\n但接觸隻game發覺 動畫內容連隻game十份一都唔知有冇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw 11章開始大家爆大鑊 <br />\n世莉架都終於交代曬所有野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntaku同主角個男同學同細妹同世莉架都慘撚到傻<br />\n屌你老母志倉個腦係咪裝屎<br />\n個同學同taku道歉話自己殺左細妹果part真係睇到眼濕濕<br />\n<br />\n仲有就係世莉架絕世好女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假如其中一個end係世莉架消失or死 <br />\n我諗我會考慮放棄黎緊幾次古戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我開始覺得套野質素上有命運石之門水準或之上</span>"},{"pid":"467e27df23bf0487b6dd793249742ef39f6d2106","tid":2027600,"uid":34293,"li